    <title type="html"><![CDATA[[簡單做]- 用PhotoShop 和 iMovie 做LomoKino牌小電影-iMovie & 成品]]></title>
    <link href="http://ccaloha.cc/blog/2011/11/10/lomokino-how-to-make-lomokino-movie-photoshop-and-imovie-part-2/"/>
    <updated>2011-11-10T11:35:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://ccaloha.cc/blog/2011/11/10/lomokino-how-to-make-lomokino-movie-photoshop-and-imovie-part-2</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>製作iMovie吧</strong></p>

<p>這邊主要是影片一開始設定的地方要注意！</p>

<ol type="a">
<li>新增專案</li>
</ol>


<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alohacc/6329879479/" title="Flickr 上 aloooooooooooha 的 螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.30.25"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6226/6329879479_19009a38bb_b.jpg" width="1024" height="640" alt="螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.30.25"></a></p>

<ol type="a">
<li>記得格率選擇"24fps-電影"</li>
</ol>


<!--more-->


<p>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alohacc/6330632392/" title="Flickr 上 aloooooooooooha 的 螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.30.40"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6225/6330632392_ecdf097b4c_b.jpg" width="1024" height="640" alt="螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.30.40"></a></p>

<ol type="a">
<li>進去計劃案之前，先編輯計劃案屬性</li>
</ol>


<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alohacc/6330632492/" title="Flickr 上 aloooooooooooha 的 螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.31.02"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6239/6330632492_1300b11260_b.jpg" width="1024" height="640" alt="螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.31.02"></a></p>

<ol type="a">
<li>把“開始的相片佈置” 設為符合影格</li>
</ol>


<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alohacc/6330632626/" title="Flickr 上 aloooooooooooha 的 螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.31.13"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6103/6330632626_9d87209ab7_b.jpg" width="1024" height="640" alt="螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.31.13"></a></p>

<ol type="a">
<li>點進去計劃案吧～ 把照片都丟進去</li>
</ol>


<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alohacc/6329880009/" title="Flickr 上 aloooooooooooha 的 螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.32.02"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6229/6329880009_edb52e7ea9_b.jpg" width="1024" height="640" alt="螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.32.02"></a></p>

<ol type="a">
<li><p>點選照片兩下之後，調整每張照片時間，你可以勾選套用套所有照片</p>

<p>我是把他設成0.3秒</p></li>
</ol>


<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alohacc/6329880179/" title="Flickr 上 aloooooooooooha 的 螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.36.38"><img src="http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6043/6329880179_f39003d4bc_b.jpg" width="1024" height="640" alt="螢幕快照 2011-11-10 上午8.36.38"></a></p>

<ol type="a">
<li>恭喜啦！加上音樂字幕～～就完成了！！！</li>
</ol>


<p>成品請看</p>

<iframe width="1280" height="720" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/6S1TS-RGt60" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>



]]></content>
